spec_data.Name: libetonyek
spec_data.Description:
libetonyek is library for import of documents from Apple iWork applications
(Keynote, Pages and Numbers). It can import documents created by
Keynote 2-6, Pages 1-4 and Numbers 1-2. The support for Numbers is rather
minimal at the moment.

spec_data.Summary: A library for import of Apple iWork documents
